    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113140/extras/b2181b891aefa8f5017cf04aba27fdac.poster.avif?t=1748811556\" width=600 height=152 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113140/extras/b2181b891aefa8f5017cf04aba27fdac.webm?t=1748811556\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113140/extras/b2181b891aefa8f5017cf04aba27fdac.mp4?t=1748811556\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>HU-man Dungeon is the most accurate HU-man simulator available to date. We have spent countless clock cycles tuning and tweaking HU-man's undignified movements and primitive combat. Even more effort was put into ensuring that every detail of HU-man’s world and customs was captured, all based on the Compendium's latest research! <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113140/extras/54533c06a02a4d5affd4065987b846e1.webp?t=1748811556\" width=615 height=32 /></span><br>On his daily hunt for tacos, treasures, and something called trombones, HU-man descended to the depths of the dungeons. We are still researching what trombones were, but in the mean time, why don’t you choose one of our 1,048,576 procedurally generated dungeons filled with enemies, traps, and treasures? Be like a HU-man! <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113140/extras/d01ddeab8979735be9f0db4cd6ca6ad1.webp?t=1748811556\" width=615 height=32 /></span><br>Take your pick of any of the three HU-man that used to inhabit our planet. Imagine being alone, disconnected from everyone, without even access to the all-knowing Compendium! <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113140/extras/ec022b0262a8d91c26b5185c0e091015.webp?t=1748811556\" width=615 height=32 /></span><br>Unlike us glorious bots, HU-man was weak without weapons to defend themselves. We have replicated most of the weapons used by HU-man down to the smallest detail like their color and scent! <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113140/extras/ad43200d6d97a13546b72d266d7a26cb.webp?t=1748811556\" width=615 height=32 /></span><br>In addition to weapons, HU-man used spells like fireballs and lightning bolts on his quest into the dungeon. Spells were colorful, effective, and efficient. My favorite! <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113140/extras/b262d10887fd3e5c72011a8d0e6032cc.webp?t=1748811556\" width=615 height=32 /></span><br>With tacos and more than three other foods readily available, find out for yourself why HU-man went crazy for cold beans! <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113140/extras/b1b43cc8da5d9cdadf34e784cc1dcc9a.webp?t=1748811556\" width=615 height=32 /></span><br>Enjoy a direct uplink to the Compendium, the last remaining one of our founding AIs! He will guide you through every dungeons, explain HU-man’s customs and difficulties, step by step! It is an honor to have him pay such close attention to our research!",
